			<span class="author"><span class="authors"><a href="http://www.theatlantic.com/taylor-clark/" class="author" >Taylor Clark</a></span></span>
		</div><!-- /linkContent -->
		<div class="linkContent">
			<a href="http://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/1969/12/american-mozart/8931/"><img src="http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/easel/images/navbars/094908_kanye-nav.jpg" alt="The Genius of Kanye West" title="The Genius of Kanye West" width="55" /></a>
			
			<h4 class="headline"><a href="http://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/1969/12/american-mozart/8931/">The Genius of Kanye West</a></h4>

			<span class="author"><span class="authors"><a href="http://www.theatlantic.com/david-samuels/" class="author" >David Samuels</a></span></span>
